title: Coast Guard suspends search for possible overboard ferry passenger in Puget Sound, Wash. (USCG - ...
text: ( Source : USCG - United States Coast Guard ) SEATTLE - The Coast Guard suspended their search for a possible man overboard after confirming with ferry staff no one had gone missing from their vessel during it's sailing in Puget Sound, Wash. ,
